1.grid
  grid is 2D , it means we have both rows and columns
  instesd of using float and positioning we are using grid

inside cont
  display:grid -- it gives content in rows and columns
  grid-template-columns-- % px fr(fraction)--- it is for width
  grid-template-row --- to give height

  grid-column-gap--- to give space between column

inside child
  grid-column-start --column no start/column no end
